      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) is commercially licensed with documented verification test suite. Version-controlled input decks and run scripts are maintained in a Git repository with tagged releases. SQA procedures satisfy MRL 2 requirements: regression tests pass, change-control log current.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
